     __________________________________________________________________

   A categorized community-driven collection of awesome Ruby libraries,
   tools, frameworks and software. The essential Ruby to build modern Apps
   and Web Apps.

   Sharing, suggestions and contributions are always welcome! Please take
   a look at the
   [https://github.com/markets/awesome-ruby/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md]co
   ntribution guidelines and quality standard first.

   Thanks to all
   [https://github.com/markets/awesome-ruby/graphs/contributors]contributo
   rs, you're awesome and this wouldn't be possible without you!
