       handling for Rails.
     * [https://github.com/seamusabshere/upsert]Upsert - Upsert on MySQL,
       PostgreSQL, and SQLite3. Transparently creates functions (UDF) for
       MySQL and PostgreSQL; on SQLite3, uses INSERT OR IGNORE.
     * [https://github.com/customink/secondbase]SecondBase - Seamless
       second database integration for Rails. SecondBase provides support
